    {
      "id": "48",
      "name": "Skill",
      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "talent",
          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Normal Attack</span></p><p>Mengakibatkan 2 poin<span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Physical DMG</span>.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/07/19/15595270/10316b5178d5109d597f415d6e7903dc_402533860634079354.png",
                "key": "Blunt Refusal",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "geo"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Blunt Refusal"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Elemental Skill</span></p><p>Mengakibatkan 3 poin <span style=\"color: #FFE699\">Geo DMG</span>. Karakter ini memperoleh status <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Geo Infusion</span>. Mem<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">buang</span> maksimum 5 kartu <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Crystal Shrapnel</span> dari Tangan dan setiap 1 kartu yang di<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">buang</span> mengakibatkan DMG ini +1 serta mengambil 1 kartu.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #ECE5D8\">Geo Infusion </span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Status</span></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Physical DMG</span> yang diakibatkan Karakter yang terpengaruh ini berubah menjadi <span style=\"color: #FFE699\">Geo DMG</span>.</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Durasi (Ronde): 2</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/07/19/15595270/d13eff9275ac9df191b4e1f83bdd18c7_7845854786926202478.png",
                "key": "Ceremonial Crystalshot",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "geo"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Ceremonial Crystalshot"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Elemental Burst</span></p><p>Mengakibatkan 1 poin <span style=\"color: #FFE699\">Geo DMG</span> dan mengakibatkan 1 poin <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Piercing DMG</span> ke semua Karakter standby lawan. Memanggil <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Rosula Dorata Salute</span> dan menciptakan 1 kartu <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Crystal Shrapnel</span> lalu ditambahkan ke Tanganmu.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/07/19/15595270/25547c6b405dc204653b701c121b1096_1816587795816822895.png",
                "key": "As the Sunlit Sky's Singing Salute ",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "geo"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "As the Sunlit Sky's Singing Salute "
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Passive Skill</span></p><p>[Pasif] <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Setelah Karakter lawan menerima DMG Reaksi Crystallize:</span> menciptakan 3 kartu<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\"> Crystal Shrapnel</span> dan dimasukkan secara acak ke dalam Dek-mu.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/07/19/15595270/7e023ac7d7c52126ccbea78e74621bfd_53584342185312656.png",
                "key": "Mutual Assistance Network",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Mutual Assistance Network"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Kartu Peristiwa</span></p><p>Mengakibatkan 1 poin <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Physical DMG</span> kepada Karakter aktif lawan dan mengambil 1 kartu.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/07/19/15595270/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_2194535867125772154.png",
                "key": "Crystal Shrapnel",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "white"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/07/19/15595270/ca5315848113a22db13d032f358ddbdb_2488420718650148994.png",
                "title": "Crystal Shrapnel"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Panggilan</span></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Tahap Selesai:</span></p><p>mengakibatkan 1 poin <span style=\"color: #FFE699\">Geo DMG</span> dan mengambil 1 kartu <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Crystal Shrapnel</span>.</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Penggunaan: 2</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/07/19/15595270/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_7155586534128248900.png",
                "key": "Rosula Dorata Salute",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/07/19/15595270/1e170b966fa674e494fba2732677bcd8_4498794995785785025.png",
                "title": "Rosula Dorata Salute"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>Bereaksi dengan Elemen jika sudah diberikan:<br>[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 153)\">Geo</span> + <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Cryo Crystallize</span>: DMG +1 poin untuk kasus ini, Karakter aktifmu memperoleh 1 poin Perisai (Dapat ditumpuk, maksimum 2 poin)</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 153)\">Geo</span> + <span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Hydro Crystallize</span>: DMG +1 poin untuk kasus ini, Karakter aktifmu memperoleh 1 poin Perisai (Dapat ditumpuk, maksimum 2 poin)</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 153)\">Geo</span> + <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Pyro Crystallize</span>: DMG +1 poin untuk kasus ini, Karakter aktifmu memperoleh 1 poin Perisai (Dapat ditumpuk, maksimum 2 poin)</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 153)\">Geo</span> + <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Electro Crystallize</span>: DMG +1 poin untuk kasus ini, Karakter aktifmu memperoleh 1 poin Perisai (Dapat ditumpuk, maksimum 2 poin)</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/07/19/15595270/fd37cbfdd3b1b2c16e6e83fb0aa96889_631124548058225879.png",
                "key": "Geo DMG",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Geo DMG"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Physical DMG</span></strong></p><p>Physical DMG tidak dapat memberikan elemen apa pun dan memicu Reaksi Elemental.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Buang</span></strong></p><p>Gunakan efek Kartu Aksi atau Skill Karakter untuk membuang Kartu Aksi dari Tangan atau Dek-mu.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Piercing DMG</span></strong></p><p>Piercing DMG tidak dapat dipengaruhi oleh Bonus DMG apa pun, namun tidak dapat ditahan oleh efek seperti Perisai atau kekebalan DMG.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Penggunaan</span></strong></p><p>Setelah efek kartu ini dipicu, 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Penggunaan</span>-nya akan dikonsumsi.</p><p>Kartu ini akan langsung dibuang setelah semua <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Penggunaan</span> telah dikonsumsi.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Durasi (Ronde)</span></strong></p><p>Setiap kali kamu mencapai Tahap Selesai di setiap Ronde, <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Durasi (Ronde)</span> -1.</p><p>Kartu ini akan langsung dibuang setelah <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Durasi (Ronde)</span> habis.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/07/19/15595270/245c229cf6f7364c7c9a7aea3db1a1ad_5697792635776843958.png",
                "key": "Detail Peraturan",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Detail Peraturan"
              }
            ]
          }
        }
      ]
